      <title>加拿大住房部长辞去特鲁多内阁职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canada-s-housing-minister-resigns-from-trudeau-s-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大住房部长肖恩·弗雷泽 (Sean Fraser) 将辞去内阁职务，并且不打算参加下次选举。2025 年大选迫在眉睫，贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 领导的自由党在民意调查中支持率低迷，因此他做出了这一决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canada-s-housing-minister-resigns-from-trudeau-s-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 02:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平称执政党内部冲突“不可避免”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/xi-says-inevitable-for-ruling-party-to-have-internal-conflicts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据中国国家主席习近平今年 1 月在一次反腐败会议上发表的最新讲话，他表示，执政党共产党内部的分裂不可避免，同时呼吁加大力度建立纪律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/xi-says-inevitable-for-ruling-party-to-have-internal-conflicts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 01:52:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尹永哲加入韩国失势总统名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/yoon-joins-growing-list-of-korean-presidents-purged-from-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统尹锡烈的去世可能来得突然、令人震惊，但他只是越来越多掌权后命运发生转变的韩国领导人中最新的一位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/yoon-joins-growing-list-of-korean-presidents-purged-from-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 01:01:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰称贸易协议前景将推动英印业务发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/uk-india-business-boosted-by-prospect-of-trade-deal-hsbc-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司的数据显示，今年英国和印度之间的贸易蓬勃发展，因为两国企业都预计两国政府将能够达成自由贸易协定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/uk-india-business-boosted-by-prospect-of-trade-deal-hsbc-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行将考虑加息 但认为采取行动的紧迫性不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/boj-set-to-weigh-rate-hike-while-seeing-little-urgency-to-act</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行将在本周的政策会议上讨论加息路径，官员们认为，尽管下次加息时间临近，但采取行动的紧迫性有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/boj-set-to-weigh-rate-hike-while-seeing-little-urgency-to-act</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚事实上的统治者推动改变联合国过渡路线图</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/syria-de-facto-rulers-push-for-changes-to-un-transition-road-map</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代表叙利亚事实上的统治者的机构表示，叙利亚反政府武装领导人艾哈迈德·沙雷和联合国叙利亚问题特使盖尔·佩德森讨论了重新考虑 2015 年联合国安理会关于该国政治过渡路线图的决议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/syria-de-facto-rulers-push-for-changes-to-un-transition-road-map</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 23:22:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长高级顾问辞职，加入离职潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/top-adviser-to-nyc-s-mayor-resigns-joining-wave-of-departures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长办公室周日表示，纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯的高级顾问英格丽德·刘易斯-马丁将辞职，标志着亚当斯在面临联邦腐败审判之际，其核心圈子中又有一名重要人物离职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/top-adviser-to-nyc-s-mayor-resigns-joining-wave-of-departures</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 22:12:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在欧洲最需要帮助的时候，德国却在崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-15/germany-is-unraveling-and-the-decline-threatens-to-become-irreversible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高昂的能源成本和出口下滑导致德国家庭损失了 2,500 欧元，而且这种下滑趋势有可能变得不可逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-12-15/germany-is-unraveling-and-the-decline-threatens-to-become-irreversible</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 22:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>弹劾案解除仅是昙花一现，韩元和股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/korean-won-stocks-take-spotlight-after-impeachment-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈通过弹劾投票后，韩国货币和股市回吐早盘涨幅，因为投资者的注意力从政治转移到困扰市场的广泛经济担忧上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/korean-won-stocks-take-spotlight-after-impeachment-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
