      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈被弹劾，让他最大的政治对手李在明有机会最终执掌国家大权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/yoon-s-fall-gives-nemesis-surprise-path-back-to-lead-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 09:54:00 GMT</pubDate>
